Title: cmk-update-agent: fixed two bugs related to curl download and certificate validation
Level: 1
Component: wato
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Edition: cee
State: unknown
Version: 1.4.0b3
Date: 1487772143

Agent files greater than 65kb could not get downloaded by curl. The agent got stuck.

Some older distributions had problems in the python requests module, when verifying
SSL certificates.
